wiki.summary: New York rapper Lil Tecca enlists the help of Chicago star Juice WRLD for the official remix to his May 2019 breakout hit “Ransom.” On the track, the rappers boast about the privileged lifestyles they live and reflect on their come-up in the rap game. This track marks the first collaboration between the two artists, and was leaked on August 11th, 2019. It was later officially released on August 15th, 2019, after Tecca teased the track in a post on Instagram, asking for “1000 comments” to drop the track. Read more on Last.fm.
